  "secondName": "Thunderhearted Heroine",
  "description": "The thing about discovering your destiny is that you're never truly ready. Everyone's life is average until the moment it isn't -- and none have learned this better than Antares. \n\nShe doesn't know if the Goddess influences fate itself, or if she's just very talented at stringing together coincidences, but as it would happen, her path crossed Mirai Narukami's totally by accident. By meeting her, she discovered the sinister plot of a foreign god looking to brainwash the world. \n\nAnd by discovering that plot, she found the power that slept inside her all along. The Goddess's Hope. \n\nAs timid and unsure as she is, only she can save the world.",
